"```sql\nSELECT d.forename, d.surname, ds.points\nFROM races r\nJOIN results res ON r.raceId = res.raceId\nJOIN drivers d ON res.driverId = d.driverId\nJOIN driverStandings ds ON res.raceId = ds.raceId AND res.driverId = ds.driverId\nWHERE r.name = 'Chinese Grand Prix' AND r.year = 2017\nORDER BY ds.points DESC\nLIMIT 3;\n```\n\nThis SQL query retrieves the top 3 drivers and the points they scored in the 2017 Chinese Grand Prix. It joins the `races`, `results`, `drivers`, and `driverStandings` tables to get the necessary information, filters for the specific race, and orders the results by points in descending order to get the top 3."